text:
Bhai,
You are simply the most chaapu guy I have ever met. Tere dimag alag level peh chalta hai bro.. I can only dream of being like you. With all the intelligence and everything, tu kaafi humble bhi hai with a very good heart. I fondly remember jab mera 3rd sem chuda tha tab tere motivation nai wapas confidence gain karne mai kaafi help kiya. Thanks for clearing all those CS220 doubts and thanks for helping with your advice whenever I needed it. I am in-dept to IITK for meeting an awesome person like you. 

Let's talk soon.
author: Harsh  Agarwal

text:
Dugu bhai!
"Sabse chaapu banda of IITK", and I am proud to call you bhai. I think hamari sabse pehli baat tempo book karne ke liye hui thi (first year endsem). Then TA201 team mates. Uske baad se sab kuch sath hi kiya. And tab se abhi tak we have become best of best friends. 

Teri tareef toh kya hi karu, but tera dedication is beyond praise. Itna motivation lata kahan se hai bhai? Also tera honest criticism, I love it and hate it at the same time. ğŸ˜‚ 

I also appreciate tera sab kuch share karna mere sath, tere saare secrets ya tera next move. Makes me think I am important to you. Seriously thanks for that! ğŸ˜Š

Goa trip was incomplete without you. I hope ki August wala trip ho. And I'm gonna try my best to make it happen. 

Touch mai toh rahenge hi bas Europe jaake bhul maat jana. Also, I know tu Palantir hi join karega. But I am secretly wishing for some magic, ki tu Korea aa jaye (I know I'm being selfish ğŸ˜› ) 

PS: Waiting for the first copy of your debut novel
author: Harsh  Agarwal

text:
Yo bhai, 
Poore IITK mai I have known you for the longest time. And I have seen you become a better version of yourself over 5 years, following the same principles. 

Kaafi fond memories hai apni. Including Freshers dance, first year mai PHY103 ka depression (kya mast gaali dete thee haam prof ko), CSE courses ke assignment, ICPC, Nutanix (mc Suyansh) kaafi kuch sath sath hi kiya hai. How can I forget the birthday treats, tune hamesha birthday treat diya hai mujhe. I kinda feel sad ki mai tujhe kabhi treat nahi diya (hopefully sometime in future).

Goa trip mai toh alag hi maza aya. Lakin May wala plan cancel ko gaya, let's hope for AugustğŸ¤.

Btw, mad respect for your eagerness to go into Quantum Computing. Only few people know ki tune kitna effort maara hai. Finally, all the best for your journey at Oxford. I know tu acha hi karega. 

Baaki touch mai toh rahenge hi. Asani se bhulne nahi dunga. ğŸ˜›
 
PS: Bhai quantum wagrah toh sab theek hai, standup comedy zarur try karna lakin. I want to see you rocking the stage. ğŸ˜‡
